OL,5, Durham University has defended its     
OL,6, decision to offer training sessions to 
OL,7, help students involved in sex work.    
OL,9,FFurther Education Minister Michelle    
OL,10,FDonelan had accused it of "legitimising
OL,11,Fa dangerous industry which thrives on  
OL,12,Fthe exploitation of women".            
OL,14,FBut the university said it was acting  
OL,15,Fresponsibly by offering students advice
OL,16,Fon how to stay safe.                   
OL,18,FLast week its students' union offered  
OL,19,Fstaff and students guidance for people 
OL,20,Finvolved in the sex industry.          
